SUMMARY:Tesla Owners at Smiles for Miles 2026
DESCRIPTION:Join fellow Tesla Owners for a fun day out with this regional e
 vent at Hardwick Hall and have an action-packed day of Inclusive automotiv
 e excitement while raising funds for JPC Community Hub CIC\, now proudly b
 ased at the TAD Centre\, Middlesbrough. JPC Community Hub continues its mi
 ssion to support individuals with special and complex needs\, live indepen
 dently and your participation helps make that possible. The Smiles for Mil
 es theme returns for 2026\, featuring an impressive range of Prestige\, Sp
 orts\, and Supercars on display. Guests can enjoy the atmosphere on-site o
 r take part in Passenger Ride Experiences along a pre-selected route off-s
 ite. Display tickets can be bought directly from the organisers: Click her
 e to get your ticket (scroll down and select "Teeside Tesla") Event highli
 ghts Hundreds of performance cars on display Sports & Supercar passenger r
 ides Special guests This event raises vital community funds Passenger Ride
  Experiences Fancy being a passenger in a performance\, sports or supercar
 ? Now’s your chance to enjoy a 5 mile drive (off-site) on a pre-selected r
 oute. You’ll have the opportunity to ride shotgun in a wide selection of p
 erformance cars\, including the likes of Ferrari\, Porsche\, McLaren\, Lam
 borghini and Aston Martin – to name but a few. Passenger rides start from 
 £25 and are available to book right now (see below) – and the best bit\, i
 t’s all for a good cause and it’s an inclusive family event. Places are li
 mited for the passenger rides experiences of around 75 per hour. Starting 
 at 10am with last rides at 4pm. Please note\, there is age restriction of 
 8+. Booster seats are available. Tickets are direct from the organiser. St
 andard Prices: Family Ticket 2 Adults & 2 Children (Under 16 years old) fo
 r £35. Adults £15 / Children (Under 16 years old) £5. VIP Parking £25 (The
 re is limited availability). There is also offsite parking opposite Hardwi
 ck Park from £5.\n\nListing: May 31st\, 2026\n\nWall clock / source TZ: Eu
 rope/London\n\nEvent & tickets (Ti.to): https://ti.to/teslaownersuk/tesla-
 owners-at-smiles-for-miles-2026\n\nSource list: upcoming\n\nTi.to DTSTAMP:
  2026-05-06T22:19:10+00:00\n\nTesla Owners UK: https://ti.to/teslaownersuk
 \n\nClub site: https://teslaowners.uk/
