SUMMARY:Tesla Gigafactory Berlin Tour 2026
DESCRIPTION:Tesla has invited the official owners club of the United Kingdo
 m to a private tour of their Gigafactory Berlin-Brandenburg for 2026. We m
 eet in Berlin on Sunday 18 October for our club reception and dinner\, and
  the have the factory tour in the morning of Monday 19 October. This makes
  it flexible for a long weekend visit or tagging onto a longer road trip. 
 We will open the registration portal by the end of April for our paid supp
 orter members\, please look out for the email and Facebook announcement. W
 e expect to be over subscribed again so priority will be given to those th
 at have not had a chance to visit the factory yet. Over 18s only. No press
  or media\; this is a special visit for TOUK members.\n\nListing: October 
 19th\, 2026\n\nWall clock / source TZ: Europe/London\n\nEvent & tickets (T
 i.to): https://ti.to/teslaownersuk/tesla-gigafactory-berlin-tour-2026\n\nS
 ource list: upcoming\n\nTi.to DTSTAMP: 2026-05-06T22:19:14+00:00\n\nTesla 
